document_data.name: Ensibal Threen
document_data.mainbody: '''Ensibal Threen''' was a mild-mannered [[War Wizards|War Wizard]] who was stabbed in the throat in [[1369 DR]] by [[Ammanadas Silversword]], who believed him to support [[Vangerdahast]]'s proposed regency.
